## BlocListener — For Actions

```dart
BlocListener<SubmitCubit, AsyncState<bool>>(
  listener: (context, state) {
    if (state.isSuccess) {
      MessageUtils.showSnackBar(message: LocaleKeys.success.tr(), baseStatus: BaseStatus.success);
      Go.back();
    }
  },
  child: bodyWidget,
)
```

