## Pagination — PaginatedCubit

```dart
PaginatedListWidget<ItemEntity>(
  cubit: context.read<ItemsCubit>(),
  itemBuilder: (item) => ItemCard(item: item),
  skeletonBuilder: () => const ItemCardSkeleton(),
)
```

